http://www.lediypourlesnuls.com/kilo-cereal-milk/ - knew i recognized this...&#xD;
i've mixed this recipe a few times as a starting point. side by side it's missing an orange-ish flavor. lemon is too strong. 3% cream fresh is a bit weird. the milk isn't close. &#xD;
rated a 3 because as far as a clone goes it's wildly different but it still comes out as a good cereal.
